{"tid":1186614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"低胸兼出股惑　大媽與廢老勁歌熱舞　收近1000元打賞？","createTime":"2019-06-05T05:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T09:56:48.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"27df45df50ebd894f06fbd9bd1c1fa5dcc7da5b5","tid":1186614,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:07:24.000Z","msg":"低胸兼出股惑 大媽與阿伯勁歌熱舞 收近1000元打賞？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HXgoyG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HXgoyG&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=e813b1b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HXgoyG</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190605/photo/bkn-20190605123132665-0605_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190605130324\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190605%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190605123132665-0605_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190605130324&h=9d904b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都好開心喎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n數名大媽在屯門公園「擺檔」，現場設置了不少演唱工具，包括音響、電子琴、咪、太陽傘等。有2名濃妝艷抹的大媽穿着低胸小背心、格仔貼身短裙，在公園內分別持羽扇和咪高峰勁歌熱舞，其中一人的背心上，更有簡體「愛」字的花紋。<br />\n<br />\n期間有穿着帽子、粉紅色襯衣的伯伯走近，與大媽近距離跳舞，大媽更主動屁股貼屁股，雙方笑容滿臉，將現場氣氛帶至高潮。<br />\n<br />\n另一段影片更可見現場充滿圍觀人群，大媽們一邊「扭動蛇腰」，一邊唱歌，更從觀眾的手中接過一張又一張的20港元及500港元紙幣，以及不少利是。從約2分鐘的影片估計，數名大媽總收近千元「打賞」。"},{"pid":"19f6198a4d4e62780db6f2457f207f7997ee01cc","tid":1186614,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:24:28.000Z","msg":"黃衫幾正"},{"pid":"3d6e3dcdde3c943809ba79444582ff5ac6413204","tid":1186614,"uid":69064,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"19f6198a4d4e62780db6f2457f207f7997ee01cc","tid":1186614,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:24:28.000Z","msg":"黃衫幾正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:26:10.000Z","msg":"你條垃圾收聲啦<br />\n保安狗"},{"pid":"c76f52a9754c0f4c81cf4d709212b738015efedc","tid":1186614,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:2